      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/earthquake-jolts-ehime-kochi-prefectures-southern-japan-jma-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本氣象廳稱，週三晚間日本南部發生了初步震級為 6.4 級的地震。]]></description>
